# BigWigs_TheWarWithin
A collection of BigWigs modules from **The War Within** era, including:

* Nerub-ar Palace
* Liberation of Undermine
* Manaforge Omega
* World Bosses

## Download
* <https://www.curseforge.com/wow/addons/bigwigs-thewarwithin>
* <https://addons.wago.io/addons/bigwigs-thewarwithin>
